{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/Little_Survivors_-_Whale_Drop_2.gif?t=1729296220\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help Marco and Eva dive into the pages of colorful comics to rescue animals imprisoned by the evil Glurks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Marco</strong> whistles to call for his pet dogs to charge to his aid.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Eva</strong> squeezes her pet birds to make them lay explosive eggs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ann</strong> twirls to make her cats pounce.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each character has 4 breeds to find, unlocking new powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Six secondary animals that attack automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy to control, with only one action button per character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Four chapters and an infinite mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The chapters are procedurally generated for maximum action!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The destructible environment allows you to release many monsters tactically, or by mistake, causing panic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt your own route: will you free an animal, or will you opt for a much-needed heart to regain some health?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blood can be replaced with black ink or white paint. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Little Survivors</strong> is the first game of a solo developer inspired by Franco-Belgian comics such as Asterix, Dungeon, Kid Paddle and Game Over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/Little_Survivors_-_Pet.gif?t=1729296220\" /></p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[